elationship with her.',138,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmIwYzViNjQtY2MxNC00NWEwLWI0M2YtNmUwODg2ZmViZmVhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjMwODI3NDE@.jpg',1984,'Action, Drama, Family','Tamil, Hindi','K. Nataraj',NULL,'Azhagan Tamizhmani','Ilaiyaraaja',NULL,NULL),('Thudikkum Karangal',6.3,'Rajinikanth is an auto mechanic and brother of Vijayakumar who works in Jaishankar\'s estate as a clerk. The movie portrays the events dealing with the clash between Rajini and Jaishankar. Radha is the love interest of Rajini and Y.G.Mahendran provides the comic relief. The movie was a big hit at the Box Office.',137,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzZmMWYyZTgtMDM0Ny00OTU5LThjZDctYzdiM2IyZDI4ODU0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTk3NTc2MzE@.jpg',1983,'Action','Tamil','C.V. Sridhar','C.V. Sridhar','K.R. Gangadharan','S.P. Balasubrahmanyam','Tiwari','K.R. Ramalingam'),('Adutha Varisu',5.4,'Kannan, a small-time bounty hunter, is enlisted by the crooked members of a royal zameen to find a girl to impersonate the lost heiress to the throne, so that they can usurp the zameen\'s wealth.',135,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzE3Y2JiZjgtOTZmZC00NDcyLTkxYjYtYzdjNDM4OTdlZDc4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODEzOTQwNTY@.jpg',1983,'Drama','Hindi, Telugu, Tamil','S.P. Muthuraman','Panchu Arunachalam','B.S. Dwarakish','Ilaiyaraaja','Babu','R. Vittal'),('Jeet Hamaari',4.8,'Thakur Vikram Singh (Om Shivpuri) is informed by a museum curator that an ancestral sword donated by his father has been stolen. This is important because it bore half the location of a hidden treasure. The other half is on a sword still in Singh\'s possession, and he must guard it. He finds a thief, Avvtar Singh (Madan Puri) attempting to steal the sword, and stops him. Avvtar grabs Thakur\'s son, Mohan, and escapes. He is to exchange sword for son at the black hills, but his car is stolen by a thief, who raises Mohan as his own under the name Raju. Raju (Rajnikanth) grows up to be a car thief, and eventually encounters his family as his enemies.',